This paper discusses the vulnerability of trust networks and the potential for attacks and spoofing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the dynamics of trust building, which could fall under the categories of social networks (cs.SI), control systems (cs.SY), cybernetics (cs.CY), and data structures (cs.DS).
